<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Der Erwerb neuer Produkte ist umso
befriedigender, <delay8 /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />je moderater der
Preis ist!<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="200" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="0" /><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Verzeih, <delay8 /><tag a="110" b="3" />, <delay20 />aber
